IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FIGURATIVE-SPACES.

DATA DIVISION.
01 NUM-FIELD PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 TEXT-FIELD PICTURE IS X(3).
01 ALPHA-FIELD PICTURE IS A(3).
01 ZERO-FIELD PICTURE IS Z(3).
01 SIGNED-FIELD PICTURE IS S9(2).
01 DECIMAL-FIELD PICTURE IS 9V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE 123 TO NUM-FIELD
MOVE "ABC" TO TEXT-FIELD
MOVE "ABC" TO ALPHA-FIELD
MOVE "999" TO ZERO-FIELD
MOVE 88 TO SIGNED-FIELD
MOVE 1 TO DECIMAL-FIELD
MOVE SPACES TO NUM-FIELD TEXT-FIELD ALPHA-FIELD ZERO-FIELD SIGNED-FIELD DECIMAL-FIELD.
